# Greeting Cards App

## Description
This is a simple React app that renders greeting cards dynamically using the `map()` function. It displays greeting messages along with the recipient's name.

## Learnings
- Understanding how to render lists in React using the `map()` function.
- Passing data as props to components.
- Applying basic inline CSS styling to components.
- React state management was not required in this example but could be useful for more complex functionality.
